  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_068_000026",
    "sentence": "太宗 持弓矢， 敬德 執槊，造 建德 壘下大呼致師。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_068_000027",
